00:39:45,223 --> 00:39:48,591
I also, uh, stopped by, uh,
to say that...

668
00:39:48,593 --> 00:39:51,561
that you shouldn't, um...

669
00:39:51,563 --> 00:39:53,730
you know, feel badly about...

