to make amends with me, too.

686
00:41:04,070 --> 00:41:05,803
I'm sure she does.

687
00:41:09,141 --> 00:41:10,618
Well...

688
00:41:11,711 --> 00:41:13,871
I hope it happens.

689
00:41:18,718 --> 00:41:20,250
Ohh.

690
00:41:22,355 --> 00:41:23,654
For a long time,

